DISCLAIMER:

This application is NOT a medical device and should NOT be used as the sole
means of monitoring blood glucose levels. Always verify readings with your
actual CGM device. Never make treatment decisions based solely on this app.

The authors and contributors of this software are not responsible for any
health-related consequences resulting from the use of this application.

Always consult with your healthcare provider regarding diabetes management.
